B%22title%22%3A%22Heart%20Attack%20Symptoms%20In%20Women%3A%20Spotting%20the%20Hidden%20Signs%20%26amp%3B%20How%20They%20Are%20Different%20For%20Women%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHeart%20disease%20is%20commonly%20misconstrued%20as%20a%20problem%20associated%20primarily%20with%20men%2C%20but%20studies%20have%20shown%20that%20it%20is%20far%20from%20the%20truth.%20A%20lack%20of%20awareness%2C%20research%2C%20and%20prevention%20efforts%20has%20resulted%20in%20women%20often%20silently%20suffering%20from%2C%20and%20dying%20of%2C%20preventable%20heart%20diseases.%20This%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F317906%2Fhow-to-prevent-heart-attack-detect-cardiac-symptoms-ecg-device-sanketlife-rahul-neha-rastogi-noida%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Heart%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20aim%20to%20shift%20the%20narrative%20to%20the%20often-ignored%20subject%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20heart%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELife%20was%20routine%20for%2040-year-old%20Neha%20until%20an%20incident%20shook%20her%20world.%20The%20Haridwar%20resident%20started%20experiencing%20sudden%20dizziness%20and%20fainting%20episodes%2C%20blacking%20out%20for%20a%20few%20seconds%20before%20regaining%20consciousness.%20This%20happened%20four%20to%20five%20times%20over%20two%20days.%20She%20visited%20a%20local%20doctor%20who%20advised%20her%20to%20immediately%20seek%20treatment%20from%20a%20specialist%20in%20Dehradun.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20conducting%20ECGs%20and%20other%20basic%20tests%2C%20the%20doctor%20in%20Dehradun%20realised%20that%20these%20were%20symptoms%20of%20sudden%20cardiac%20arrests%20and%20referred%20her%20to%20the%20Fortis%20Escorts%20Heart%20Institute%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20where%20she%20proceeded%20for%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Aparna%20Jaswal%2C%20Director%20of%20Cardiology%2C%20Department%20of%20Cardiac%20Pacing%20and%20Electrophysiology%20at%20Fortis%2C%20identified%20Neha%E2%80%99s%20symptoms%20as%20a%20heart%20ailment%2C%20explaining%20that%20her%20sudden%20fainting%20episodes%20were%20the%20result%20of%20cardiac%20arrest.%20They%20were%20able%20to%20identify%20the%20ailment%20through%20continuous%20heart%20monitoring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeha%E2%80%99s%20case%20is%20not%20the%20only%20one.%20The%20prevalence%20of%20coronary%20artery%20diseases%20in%20women%20range%20from%20three%20to%2013%20percent%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EJournal%20of%20the%20American%20College%20of%20Cardiology%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20report%20also%20states%20that%20the%20disease%20has%20increased%20by%20over%20300%20percent%20in%20the%20past%2020%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Global%20Burden%20of%20Disease%20Study%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341755%2Fcongenital-heart-disease-in-babies-treatment-surgery-provided-by-hans-foundation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheart%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20leading%20cause%20of%20fatality%20among%20Indian%20women%2C%20accounting%20for%20over%2017%20percent%20of%20deaths.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20alarming%20statistic%20underscores%20the%20importance%20of%20recognising%20the%20unique%20ways%20heart%20diseases%20manifest%20in%20women%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20critical%20need%20for%20awareness%20and%20proactive%20health%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHeart%20disease%20is%20the%20biggest%20killer%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeart%20disease%20refers%20to%20a%20range%20of%20conditions%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F336492%2Fgoan-artist-xavier-fernandes-makes-christmas-cribs-from-driftwood%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoronary%20artery%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20congenital%20heart%20disease%2C%20arrhythmia%20(irregular%20heartbeats)%2C%20cardiac%20arrest%2C%20and%20more.%20It%20is%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20causes%20of%20death%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20more%20often%20than%20not%2C%20heart%20diseases%20are%20preventable%20and%20can%20be%20successfully%20treated%20if%20diagnosed%20early.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20traditional%20belief%20is%20that%20heart%20diseases%20generally%20affect%20women%2010%20years%20later%20than%20men%2C%20this%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20case.%20Just%20like%20younger%20men%20are%20getting%20heart%20attacks%2C%20so%20are%20women%2C%20but%20they%20are%20often%20unaware%20of%20the%20signs%20and%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fheart-care-1040227_1280-1727414916.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fheart-care-1040227_1280-1727414916.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fheart-care-1040227_1280-1727414916-300x212.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fheart-care-1040227_1280-1727414916-500x354.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fheart-care-1040227_1280-1727414916-768x543.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fheart-care-1040227_1280-1727414916-150x106.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367768%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22905%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20doctors%2C%20the%20first%20vital%20step%20is%20to%20address%20a%20common%20misconception%20that%20cardiovascular%20diseases%2C%20including%20heart%20attacks%2C%20affect%20men%20more%20than%20women.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20critical%20difference%20is%20that%20women%20often%20experience%20%E2%80%98silent%E2%80%99%20heart%20diseases%2C%20where%20symptoms%20may%20not%20be%20as%20pronounced%20or%20may%20be%20misattributed%20to%20other%20conditions.%20This%20often%20leads%20to%20delays%20in%20diagnosis%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Ravinder%20Singh%20Rao%2C%20an%20interventional%20structural%20cardiologist%20and%20angioplasty%20expert.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20for%20women%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20symptoms%20and%20to%20seek%20immediate%20hospital%20care%20whenever%20they%20experience%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESymptoms%20of%20a%20heart%20attack%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20usual%20symptoms%20common%20across%20genders%20include%20chest%20pain%2C%20pressure%20or%20discomfort%20that%20lasts%20more%20than%20a%20few%20minutes%20or%20recurs%2C%20Dr%20Rao%20informs.%20However%2C%20he%20adds%20that%20chest%20pain%20experienced%20by%20women%20may%20differ%20slightly%20from%20that%20experienced%20by%20men%2C%20often%20described%20more%20as%20pressure%20or%20tightness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COther%20symptoms%20seen%20in%20women%20include%20neck%2C%20jaw%20and%20shoulder%20pain%2C%20shortness%20of%20breath%2C%20pain%20in%20one%20or%20both%20arms%2C%20nausea%20or%20vomiting%2C%20sweating%2C%20or%20dizziness.%20Women%20should%20be%20particularly%20cautious%20about%20atypical%20symptoms%2C%20as%20they%20may%20not%20be%20recognised%20as%20signs%20of%20a%20heart%20attack%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Jaswal%20adds%20that%20dizziness%2C%20blurring%20or%20fainting%2C%20radiating%20pain%20to%20the%20shoulders%20and%20jaw%2C%20extreme%20fatigue%20or%20breathlessness%2C%20and%20palpitations%20are%20also%20symptoms%20seen%20in%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-3-17274