20disease.%20If%20any%20of%20these%20levels%20are%20elevated%2C%20treat%20them%20on%20time.%20Heart%20diseases%20are%20preventable%20if%20these%20risk%20factors%20are%20in%20check%20and%20monitored%20regularly%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Jaswal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20risk%20factors%20for%20women%20include%20pregnancy%20complications.%20If%20a%20woman%20has%20gestational%20diabetes%20or%20preeclampsia%20(high%20blood%20pressure)%2C%20the%20risk%20of%20heart%20disease%20later%20increases.%20Therefore%2C%20doctors%20stress%20that%20it%20is%20vital%20for%20women%20of%20all%20ages%20to%20prioritise%20their%20heart%20health.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20World%20Heart%20Federation%2C%20women%20also%20tend%20to%20have%20more%20severe%20first%20heart%20attacks%20that%20more%20frequently%20lead%20to%20death%20compared%20to%20men.%20%E2%80%9CWomen%20are%20the%20forefront%20and%20backbone%20of%20the%20family.%20Yet%2C%20they%20quietly%20die%20due%20to%20sudden%20cardiac%20arrests%2C%20and%20not%20much%20is%20spoken%20about%20it.%20It%E2%80%99s%20time%20that%20women%20recognise%20the%20warning%20signs%20and%20rush%20to%20the%20hospital%20any%20time%20they%20experience%20any%20of%20the%20symptoms%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Jaswal%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20urges%20women%20to%20have%20yearly%20health%20check-ups%20and%20take%20immediate%20action%20if%20any%20of%20their%20levels%20are%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeha%E2%80%99s%20prompt%20thinking%20probably%20saved%20her%20life.%20You%20too%20can%20save%20yours%20by%20taking%20care%20of%20your%20health%20and%20acting%20promptly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTime%20is%20critical%20during%20a%20heart%20attack%2C%20and%20even%20a%20minute%20can%20turn%20the%20situation%20around%20for%20a%C2%A0%20person.%20In%20crucial%20times%2C%20you%20should%20trust%20your%20instincts%2C%20and%20if%20something%20feels%20wrong%2C%20you%20should%20immediately%20seek%20medical%20attention%2C%E2%80%9D%20say