%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20drama%20today%20carries%20over%20from%20Thursday%20night%2C%20when%20Mr%20Saxena%20insisted%20the%20election%20be%20held%20at%2010%20pm.%20The%20AAP%20refused%3B%20Mr%20Sisodia%20slammed%20the%20late-night%20vote%20he%20said%20was%20called%20at%20an%20hour's%20notice.%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20elections%20be%20held...%20AAP%2C%20Congress%20councillors%20have%20gone%20home...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20Mayor%20Oberoi%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20written%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Commissioner%20(of%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi)%20that%20the%20election%20to%20be%20held%20today%20is%20unconstitutional%20and%20illegal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Mr%20Saxena%20sought%20to%20overturn%20that%20order%2C%20demanding%20MCD%20Commissioner%20Ashwini%20Kumar%20%26quot%3Bsubmit%20a%20report%20of%20conduct%20of%20elections...%20by%2010%20pm%20today%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20Deputy%20Mayor%20oversee%20proceedings%20if%20Ms%20Oberoi%20declares%20herself%20unavailable%20for%20any%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-lt-governor-overturns-deferring-of-standing-committee-seat-election-6657386%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDelhi%20Lt%20Governor%20Nixes%20Deferring%20Of%20Standing%20Committee%20Seat%20Election%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MCD%20Standing%20Committee%20takes%20most%20of%20its%20financial%20decisions.%20At%20present%20it%20has%20three%20AAP%20members%20and%20two%20from%20the%20opposition%20BJP%2C%20giving%20the%20ruling%20party%20control%20of%20the%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appointment%20of%20a%20sixth%20member%20-%20pending%20for%20months%20-%20could%20break%20the%20tie%20in%20the%20BJP's%20favour.%20The%20AAP%20has%20alleged%20the%20order%20for%20last%20night's%20election%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20do%20just%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20demanded%