20in%202006%20sent%20shockwaves%20across%20India%2C%20instilling%20fear%20and%20horror%20in%20many.%20The%20recent%20Netflix%20film%2C%20%3Cem%3ESector%2036%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20is%20unofficially%20inspired%20by%20this%20tragic%20event%2C%20which%20involved%20the%20kidnapping%20and%20murder%20of%20numerous%20children%20and%20women.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Obsession%20With%20Gory%20Details%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20uncommon%20for%20filmmakers%20to%20draw%20from%20real-life%20tragedies.%20But%20debutant%20director%20Aditya%20Nimbalkar%20and%20writer%20Bodhayan%20Raychaudhuri's%20film%2C%20released%20on%20September%2013%2C%20perhaps%20seem%20to%20forget%20how%20profound%20a%20human%20tragedy%20the%20Nithari%20killings%20were.%20The%20film%20trivialises%20the%20case%20through%20its%20poorly%20developed%20characters%20and%20overtly%20graphic%20depictions%20of%20murder%2C%20sexual%20abuse%2C%20necrophilia%2C%20and%20cannibalism.%20Sensational%20and%20brutal%2C%20it%20presents%20nauseatingly%20grotesque%20portrayals%20of%20its%20victims.%C2%A0%20As%20the%20story%20unfolds%2C%20it%20becomes%20evident%20that%20the%20filmmakers%2C%20lacking%20any%20social%20consciousness%2C%20appear%20more%20obsessed%20with%20shocking%20viewers%20with%20dismembered%20and%20decaying%20body%20parts%20on-screen%20rather%20than%20with%20exploring%20the%20human%20aspects%20of%20the%20story.%20Featuring%20Vikrant%20Massey%20as%20the%20psychopathic%20butcher%20Prem%2C%20Akash%20Khurana%20as%20his%20wealthy%20employer%20Bassi%2C%20and%20Deepak%20Boriyal%20as%20SI%20Ram%20Charan%20Pandey%2C%20the%20investigator%2C%20the%20film%20betrays%20a%20severe%20lack%20of%20thoughtful%20examination%20of%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20outset%2C%20%3Cem%3ESector%2036%3C%2Fem%3E's%20narrative%20is%20centred%20around%20disturbing%20scenes%2C%20including%20ones%20where%20Prem%20is%20seen%20butchering%20a%20schoolgirl%20in%20a%20restroom.%20The%20treatment%20raises%20a%20few%20critical%20questions%3A%20what%20was%20the%20intention%20behind%20creating%20Sector%2036%3F%20How%20can%20a%20real-life%20horror%20story%20be%20reduced%20to%20a%20mere%20spectacle%3F%20And%20in%20what%20way%20does%20this%20film%20qualify%20as%20entertainment%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EShould%20OTT%20Face%20Regulation%20Too%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStreaming%20platforms%20have%20long%20had%20an%20affinity%20towards%20true%20crime%20stories%20and%20films%20based%20on%20unsolved%20murders%2C%20sensational%20cases%2C%20and%20freak%20accidents.%20Millions%20are%20invested%20in%20such%20productions%20solely%20because%20they%20captivate%20and%20fascinate%20audiences%20and%20drive%20profits.%20The%20entertainment%20industry%20banks%20on%20this%20very%20fascination%20and%20curiosity.%20True%2C%20many%20true%20crime%20filmmakers%20do%20make%20an%20effort%20to%20present%20a%20well-crafted%20and%20thought-provoking%20narrative.%20But%20that%20can't%20be%20said%20for%20%3Cem%3ESector%2036%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20whose%20lack%20of%20depth%20and%20research%20almost%20borders%20on%20disregard%20for%20the%20victims%20in%20the%20Nithari%20killings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20heavy%20debate%20over%20censorship%20on%20digital%20platforms%20in%20recent%20years.%20While%20the%20government%20has%20cracked%20down%20on%20content%20deemed%20vulgar%2C%20OTT%20platforms%20are%20expected%20to%20self-regulate%20their%20offerings%20in%20the%20realm%20of%20general%20entertainment.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20%3Cem%3ESector%2036%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20that%20self-regulation%20-%20and%20reflection%20-%20seem%20absent%2C%20both%20on%20the%20filmmakers'%20end%20as%20well%20as%20the%20streaming%20platform's.%20If%20shock%20value%20was%20the%20intention%20of%20the%20makers%2C%20then%20they%20have%20indeed%20succeeded%2C%20but%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20horrific%20tragedy%2C%20and%20by%20exploiting%20it%20for%20fame%20and%20profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWriters%20and%20