e%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2030%20months%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpainstaking%20efforts%E2%80%9D%20were%20directed%20towards%20retaining%20existing%20details%20that%20played%20a%20role%20in%20the%20building%E2%80%99s%20legacy%2C%20in%20a%20more%20nuanced%20fashion.%20Malik%20adds%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332749%2Fex-banker-sunando-sen-built-tanhau-sustainable-himalayan-homestay-corbett-restore-wildlife%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etouches%20of%20sustainability%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20included%20in%20every%20way%20possible.%20For%20months%2C%20the%20team%20scraped%20away%20at%20old%20plaster%2C%20which%20yielded%20brickwork%20and%20vintage%20Burma%20teak%20woodwork%20underneath.%20Look%20around%20and%20you%E2%80%99ll%20notice%20in%20some%20places%20the%20colours%20don%E2%80%99t%20quite%20match.%20Malik%20underscores%20that%20no%20attempts%20were%20made%20to%20polish%20the%20teak%20wood%20surfaces.%20This%20lends%20a%20rugged%2C%20raw%20touch%20to%20the%20staircase%20at%20the%20Native%20Restaurant%20and%20Bar%2C%20its%20roof%20structure%20and%20flooring%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Ice%20Factory%20roof%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20if%20there%20are%20mismatches%3F%20It%20only%20adds%20to%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20space%2C%20the%20architect%20believes.%20That%20being%20said%2C%20he%20adds%20that%20in%20places%20where%20it%20was%20necessitated%2C%20safety%20upgrades%20were%20made.%20These%20include%20structural%20reinforcements%20to%20the%20walls%20and%20roof.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-3_11zon-1726747460.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IF.BE%20boasts%20five%20sections%20which%20include%20a%20fine-dining%20restaurant%2C%20a%20cafe%2C%20a%20space%20for%20exhibitions%2C%20a%20space%20for%20performances%20and%20a%20reading%20room%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-3_11zon-1726747460.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-3_11zon-1726747460-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-3_11zon-1726747460-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-3_11zon-1726747460-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-3_11zon-1726747460-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366752%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIF.BE%20boasts%20five%20sections%20which%20include%20a%20fine-dining%20restaurant%2C%20a%20cafe%2C%20a%20space%20for%20exhibitions%2C%20a%20space%20for%20performances%2C%20and%20a%20reading%20room%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20space%20that%20took%20the%20most%20amount%20of%20brainstorming%2C%20Malik%20shares%2C%20was%20the%20main%20Ice%20Factory%2C%20sub-station%2C%20cold%20storage%2C%20and%20the%20ice-cubing%20area.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20required%20intensive%20examination%20and%20surgical%20intervention%20through%20retrofits%20to%20stabilise%20crumbling%2C%20warped%2C%20and%20leaking%20walls%2C%20sagging%20roofs%20and%20trusses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20in%20every%20adventure%20story%2C%20the%20most%20exciting%20part%20is%20when%20a%20treasure%20is%20discovered.%20When%20the%20team%20stumbled%20upon%20giant%20cooling%20coils%20that%20were%20once%20used%20to%20manufacture%20ice%2C%20they%20were%20thrilled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%