%20train%20to%20be%20halted%20as%20a%20precaution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20new%20engine%20had%20to%20be%20brought%20from%20Aurihar%20Railway%20Station.%20Reports%20indicate%20the%20train%20was%20delayed%20by%20nearly%20three%20hours.%20This%20happened%20early%20morning%2C%20around%203%20am%2C%20local%20media%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20police%20case%20has%20been%20filed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20reports%20of%20stones%20being%20thrown%20at%20the%20Dibrugarh-New%20Delhi%20Rajdhani%20that%20was%20travelling%20on%20the%20same%20track%2C%20but%20ahead%20of%20the%20Swatantrata%20Senani%20Express.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20not%20been%20confirmed%20as%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727412840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fcdnqb64o_train-attacked-with-stones_650x400_27_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstones-thrown-at-swatantra-express-in-bihar-some-passengers-hurt-6660158%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stones%20were%20thrown%20at%20the%20Swatantrata%20Senani%20Express%20in%20Bihar's%20Samastipur%20district%20on%20Thursday%20night%2C%20as%20it%20was%20travelling%20from%20Jainagar%20to%20New%20Delhi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstones-thrown-at-swatantra-express-in-bihar-some-passengers-hurt-6660158%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BPapa%2C%20Come%20Back%26quot%3B%3A%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20Slams%20Government%20Over%20Haryana%20Job%20Crunch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20upcoming%20Haryana%20elections%2C%20on%20Thursday%20slammed%20the%20state%20government%20in%20a%20public%20rally%20for%20the%20lack%20of%20employment%20opportunities%20that%20cause%20youth%20to%20migrate.%20During%20his%20address%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20used%20examples%20from%20the%20struggles%20of%20children%20whose%20parents%20migrate%20to%20America%20and%20get%20stuck%20there%20with%20no%20prospects%20of%20returning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha's%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20shared%20the%20story%20of%20a%20boy%20named%20Dev%2C%20who%20cried%20out%20for%20his%20father.%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDev's%20trembling%20cry%20-%20'Papa%2C%20come%20back!'%20-%20was%20heart-rending.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20noted%20that%20while%20Dev's%20cry%20might%20not%20reach%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20heart%2C%20it%20has%20impacted%20him%20deeply.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20to%20stop%20these%20cries%2C%20wipe%20these%20tears%2C%20and%20ensure%20a%20happy%20life%20with%20their%20families%20by%20giving%20proper%20opportunities%20to%20the%20youth%20of%20Haryana%20within%20the%20state%20itself%20-%20and%20we%20will%20do%20it!%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20criticised%20the%20Modi%20government%20for%20failing%20to%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20people.%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20the%20benefit%3F%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20being%20marketed%20and%20Dev%20is%20shouting%2C%20screaming%20to%20bring%20back%20his%20father.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20thinking%20that%20when%20I%20go%20home%2C%20I%20will%20send%20some%20toys%20for%20Dev.%20Then%20I%20thought%2C%20what%20do%20toys%20mean%20to%20him%3F%20What%20will%20he%20do%20with%20a%20football%3F%20What%20will%20he%20do%20with%20a%20cricket%20bat%3F%20All%20he%20wants%20is%20his%20father.%20This%20is%20the%20condition%20of%20Haryana%2C%20and%20we%20want%20to%20change%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20then%20urged%20for%20a%20change%20in%20Haryana%2C%20where%20families%20can%20live%20without%20fear%20and%20sorrow.%20He%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20such%20a%20Haryana%20where%20children%20do%20not%20cry%2C%20where%20a%20father%20can%20hug%20his%20child%20and%20a%20mother%20does%20not%20cry%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20To%20achieve%20this%2C%20he%20laid%20out%20several%20promises%2C%20including%20financial%20support%20for%20women%20and%20jobs%20for%20the%20youth.%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20first%20step%20is%20Mahila%20Shakti%2C%20Rs2000%20per%20month%20to%20women%20and%20a%20gas%20cylinder%20worth%20Rs500.%20The%20second%20step%20is%20that%20we%20will%20fill%20the%20two%20lakh%20vacancies%20that%20are%20lying%20vacant%20in%20the%20government%20for%20the%20youth%20and%20give%20them%20to%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20promised%20to%20guarantee%20Minimum%20Support%20Prices%20(MSP)%20for%20farmers%20and%20provide%20immediate%20insurance%20money%20for%20losses.%20%26quot%3BHousing%20for%20the%20poor%20will%20include%20a%20100-yard%20plot%20and%20Rs1.5%20lakh%2C%20three%20lakh%20rupees%20for%20two%20houses%2C%20two%20rooms%2C%20two%20bedrooms%2C%20and%20300%20units%20of%20free%20electricity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20warned%20of%20threats%20to%20the%20Constitution%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20fight%20is%20to%20save%20the%20Constitution.%20The%20poor%20people%20of%20India%2C%20the%20people%20of%20the%20weaker%20sections%2C%20are%20protected%20by%20the%20Constitution%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20is%20trying%20to%20destroy%20it.%26quot%3B%20He%20then%20once%20again%20reiterated%20the%20need%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20to%20understand%20the%20demographics%20of%20the%20country%20and%20how%20resources%20are%20distributed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20address%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20also%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20everyone%20in%20Haryana%20has%20to%20stand%20together%20because%20the%20tears%20of%20the%20crying%20children%20have%20to%20reach%20them%2C%20and%20they%20have%20to%20be%20made%20happy%20and%20hugged%20by%20their%20fathers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%20goes%20to%20polls%20on%20October%205%20to%20elect%20a%2090-member%20state%20legislative%20assembly%20to%20fo