sinessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-investment-bank-leaders-lay-out-winning-strategy-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20working%20in%20Singapore%20and%20Hong%20Kong%20managing%20key%20relationships%20by%20flying%20to%20a%20different%20Chinese%20city%20each%20day.%20It%20became%20exhausting%20but%20gave%20me%20insight%20into%20the%20gold%20standard%20of%20ultra-high%20net%20worth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20leaving%20finance%2C%20a%20former%20client%20called%20to%20ask%20where%20I%20was%20moving%20next%2C%20and%20I%20told%20him%20I%20was%20taking%20a%20break%20to%20plan%20my%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnglish%20wasn't%20his%20first%20language%2C%20so%20he%20misunderstood%20and%20thought%20I%20was%20starting%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwedding-planner-was-the-best-decision-i-made-2018-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewedding%20planning%3C%2Fa%3E%20business.%20He%20immediately%20asked%20me%20to%20help%20plan%20his%20son's%20wedding%2C%20insisting%20I%20take%20a%20look%20since%20I%20knew%20the%20family%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20flew%20to%20Indonesia%2C%20where%20he%20was%20based.%20When%20I%20arrived%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20see%20seven%20other%20wedding%20planners%20in%20the%20room%2C%20as%20hiring%20even%20one%20professional%20planner%20was%20rare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20was%20close%20to%20the%20family%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20plan%20the%20wedding%20and%20handle%20their%20needs%20directly%2C%20while%20other%20planners%20focused%20on%20other%20aspects%20of%20the%20wedding.%20This%20experience%20opened%20my%20eyes%20to%20the%20complexity%20of%20orchestrating%20such%20an%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20wedding%2C%20the%20word%20got%20around%20that%20I%20was%20involved%20in%20the%20planning%2C%20and%20some%20of%20my%20former%20clients%20who%20were%20there%20asked%20if%20I%20could%20plan%20their%20children's%20weddings%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20I%20started%20my%20events%20planning%20business%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.the-atelier.co%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Atelier%20%26amp%3B%20Co%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226953427d-af66-49b3-a1a4-0e8cc8df15d9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20No%20such%20thing%20as%20%26quot%3Bimpossible%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mantra%20is%20that%20anything%20is%20possible%20with%20time%20and%20resources.%20This%20mindset%20has%20kept%20me%20calm%20in%20the%20face%20of%20challenging%20requests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20unusual%20guest%20request%20once%20stumped%20my%20team%20for%20a%20wedding%20on%20a%20remote%20island%3A%20He%20insisted%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20sleep%20in%20his%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20didn't%20flinch.%20I%20just%20made%20arrangements%20for%20his%20bed%20to%20be%20transported%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%20for%20us%20not%20to%20judge%20whether%20something%20is%20necessary%20for%20the%20wedding.%20Our%20role%20is%20to%20facilitate%20and%20provide%20solutions%20to%20make%20the%20request%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20a%20wedding%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-travel-to-the-maldives-on-budget-luxury-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMaldives%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20a%20beautiful%20but%20difficult%20destination%20for%20weddings%20because%20we%20had%20to%20ship%20or%20fly%20all%20our%20logistics%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20set%20up%2C%20we%20loaded%20cranes%20and%20trucks%20onto%20an%20oil%20tanker%2C%20which%20took%2024%20hours%20to%20transport%20to%20the%20island%2C%20and%20we%20had%20multiple%20tankers%2C%20taking%20a%20week%20in%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222796%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maldives%20Wedding%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f4cc68de59ade1a3b4ad16%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELelian%20and%20her%20team%20sp