heir%20needs%20heard%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20role%20is%20to%20be%20objective%20professionals.%20I%20always%20start%20by%20meeting%20all%20our%20stakeholders%20and%20ensuring%20everyone%20has%20a%20voice%2C%20even%20though%20their%20opinions%20might%20not%20get%20incorporated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20it's%20not%20always%20possible%20to%20have%20one%20event%20that%20meets%20the%20needs%20of%20all%20stakeholders%2C%20so%20it's%20not%20uncommon%20for%20us%20to%20plan%20multiple%20events%20for%20our%20clients%2C%20from%20an%20intimate%20family%20celebration%20at%20home%20to%20a%20destination%20wedding%20party%20on%20an%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220e05db2b-b05f-4dfc-a0ad-0ec0d1e17252%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Focusing%20on%20traditions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPreserving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwedding-traditions-around-the-world-2018-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditions%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20essential%20for%20grandparents%20and%20parents%2C%20who%20want%20to%20pass%20down%20what%20they%20grew%20up%20with%20to%20the%20next%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20our%20elder%20clients%20want%20to%20see%20their%20grandchildren%20uphold%20customs%20they%20cherish%2C%20like%20family%20crests%20and%20cultural%20elements.%20For%20example%2C%20with%20the%20Chinese%2C%20there's%20a%20tea%20ceremony%20that%20we%20have%20to%20get%20right%20because%20it%20is%20a%20custom%20that%20connects%20Chinese%20elders%20to%20the%20younger%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chinese%20wedding%20betrothal%20gifts%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f4ce330d59cc64f5b0483e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGifts%20presented%20at%20a%20traditional%20Chinese%20betrothal%20ceremony%3Cp%3EThe%20Atelier%20%26amp%3B%20Co%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20want%20the%20weddin