er%20fudge%20every%20Christmas%3F%20What%20about%20the%20cookies%20they%20serve%20each%20month%20during%20your%20book%20club%20meeting%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20parent%2C%20it's%20crucial%20that%20I%20don't%20fixate%20on%20nutrition.%20Listen%2C%20as%20a%20function%20of%20my%20job%2C%20I%20know%20better%20than%20most%20how%20important%20nutrition%20is%2C%20but%20the%20hyperfixation%20on%20nutrition%20can%20also%20be%20harmful%2C%20leading%20many%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Forthorexia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eorthorexia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20or%20an%20unhealthy%20obsession%20with%20healthy%20eating.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat's%20why%20I%20intentionally%20provide%20my%20toddler%20a%20variety%20of%20foods%2C%20even%20some%20highly%20processed%20ones.%20(I'm%20looking%20at%20you%2C%20dino%20nuggets!)%20By%20doing%20so%2C%20I'm%20doing%20my%20best%20to%20prevent%20the%20development%20of%20restrictive%20eating%20habits%20later%20on%20and%20encourage%20a%20healthy%2C%20balanced%20relationship%20with%20food.%20This%20also%20keeps%20mealtimes%20realistic%2C%20offering%20foods%20my%20child%20enjoys%20and%20that%20are%20easy%20for%20our%20busy%20family.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20goal%20is%20to%20teach%20flexibility%20and%20balance.%20When%20kids%20are%20allowed%20to%20enjoy%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20foods%2C%20they%20grow%20up%20understanding%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteach-kids-destigmatize-fat-eat-food-no-judgment-moral-value-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eall%20foods%20can%20fit%20into%20a%20healthy%20lifestyle%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20rather%20than%20categorizing%20foods%20as%20%26quot%3Bgood%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bbad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2249850c67-6