e%20of%20weight-loss%20medication%20has%20left%20out%20millions%20of%20Americans%20who%20could%20benefit%2C%20as%20highlighted%20in%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fnovo-nordisk-ceo-faces-senate-questions-over-high-prices-of-ozempic-and-wegovy-in-us-1033798280%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESenate%20Committee%20Hearings%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20Novo%20Nordisk's%20CEO%20faced%20tough%20questions%20about%20its%20versions%20of%20similar%20drugs%2C%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20she%2C%20like%20many%20others%2C%20has%20found%20a%20way%20around%20the%20snarls%20of%20the%20healthcare%20system%20to%20stay%20on%20the%20drug.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b6ae44a3-53cb-4a2c-8ff1-f68263c11f64%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAt%20first%2C%20she%20tried%20the%20pharma%20solution%3A%20coupons%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20trial%20ended%2C%20Rothenhoefer's%20doctor%20issued%20her%20a%20prescription%20for%20Mounjaro%20but%20she%20knew%20she%20couldn't%20afford%20it%20with%20her%20office%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20a%20problem%2C%20manufacturer%20Eli%20Lilly%20told%20her%20%E2%80%94%20she%20could%20get%20a%20coupon%2C%20allowing%20her%20to%20access%20the%20drug%20at%20a%20steep%20discount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProviding%20coupons%20is%20a%20common%20practice%20for%20drug%20makers%20to%20incentivize%20patients%20to%20try%20their%20product%2C%20instead%20of%20a%20competitor's%2C%20especially%20when%20it's%20a%20new%20offering%20in%20an%20already-hot%20and%20high-priced%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20coupon%20expired%20in%20June%202023.%20And%20all%20she%20could%20do%20was%20ration%20out%20her%20remaining%20doses%20and%20hope%20for%20the%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20insurance%20doesn't%20cover%20it.%20Most%20people%20can't%20afford%20it.%20I%20had%20no%20choice%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229f175e6c-deef-4bd9-8285-ccf7d1bc03be%5C%22%