ole%20in%20%3Cem%3ELaapataa%20Ladies%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%94%20as%20Manju%20Mai%2C%20a%20fiercely%20independent%20tea%20stall%20owner%20%E2%80%94%20has%20become%20a%20sensation.%20Audiences%20have%20praised%20her%20nuanced%20portrayal%20of%20a%20woman%20who%20is%20tough%20yet%20compassionate.%20Manju%20Mai%2C%20hardened%20after%20facing%20betrayal%20from%20her%20abusive%20husband%20and%20the%20sacrifices%20she%20made%2C%20teaches%20Phool%20(and%20the%20viewers)%20the%20power%20of%20self-reliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Kadam%E2%80%99s%20success%20didn%E2%80%99t%20come%20overnight.%20Born%20and%20raised%20in%20Kalina%2C%20a%20suburb%20of%20Mumbai%2C%20she%20comes%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366893%2Ftruck-drivers-daughter-to-cannes-how-sunita-rajwar-brought-her-fathers-cinema-dreams-to-lifesunita-rajwar-inspiring-journey-panchayat-gullak-stree-kedarnath-movies-list-timeline-national-school-of-dra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20humble%20working-class%20background%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20her%20early%20years%2C%20she%20harboured%20dreams%20of%20playing%20kabaddi%20professionally%2C%20even%20making%20it%20to%20the%20state%20level.%20Later%2C%20she%20considered%20opening%20a%20gym%20or%20joining%20the%20police%20force%3B%20acting%20was%20never%20on%20her%20radar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F246618%2Factor-ashwath-bhatt-haider-raazi-kashmiri-students-education-inspiring-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edidn%E2%80%99t%20plan%20on%20becoming%20an%20actor%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20it%20happened%20accidentally%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20admitted.%20After%20years%20of%20working%20odd%20jobs%20and%20supporting%20her%20family%2C%20she%20found%20herself%20drawn%20to%20the%20world%20of%20Marathi%20theatre.%20Despite%20her%20enthusiasm%2C%20Kadam%E2%80%99s%20debut%20film%20never%20saw%20t