0journey%20is%20a%20mark%20of%20serendipity%3B%20right%20from%20her%20foray%20into%20the%20bachelor%20in%20design%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F114959%2Fmigrant-workers-sleep-easy-design-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eindustrial%20design%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20NID%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20initially%20preparing%20for%20my%20law%20entrance%20exam%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20to%20winning%20the%20James%20Dyson%20Award%202024%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CNovocarry%20started%20out%20as%20a%20classroom%20project.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerceived%20as%20the%20gold%20standard%20for%20design%20awards%2C%20the%20James%20Dyson%20recognition%20fosters%20problem-solving%20attitudes%2C%20encouraging%20students%20to%20broaden%20their%20innovative%20minds.%20Recalling%20her%20introduction%20to%20the%20Dyson%20world%2C%20Komal%20recalls%20seeing%20the%20famous%20hairdryer.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20fascinated%20with%20the%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20points%20out.%20Her%20excitement%20is%20still%20palpable%20through%20the%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20led%20to%20another%2C%20taking%20Komal%20down%20a%20rabbit%20hole%20of%20videos%20that%20dissected%20the%20hair%20dryer%E2%80%99s%20ergonomic%20design.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20hooked.%20It%20was%20a%20Eureka!%20moment%20that%20had%20me%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20design.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnovocarry-1726751585.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Komal%20Panda%20is%20the%20national%20winner%20of%20the%20James%20Dyson%202024%20award%20for%20her%20innovation%20Novocarry%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnovocarry-1726751585.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnovocarry-1726751585-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnovocarry-1726751585-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnovocarry-1726751585-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnovocarry-1726751585-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366790%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKomal%20Panda%20is%20the%20national%20winner%20of%20the%20James%20Dyson%202024%20award%20for%20her%20innovation%20Novocarry.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deeper%20she%20dived%2C%20the%20more%20curious%20she%20became.%20And%20now%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354461%2Fanti-microbial-water-bottles-tanks-mattresses-anasuya-roy-iit-delhi-phd-active-copper-technology%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20innovation%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20James%20Dyson-recognised%2C%20she%20is%20elated.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20announced%20the%20national%20award%20winner%2C%20it%20was%20such%20validation.%20It%20assured%20me%20that%20my%20product%20was%20not%20just%20%E2%80%98usable%E2%80%99%20but%20also%20%E2%80%98desirable%E2%80%99.%20This%20is%20special%20since%20my%20forte%20isn%E2%80%99t%20in%20engineering.%E2%80%9D%20That%20being%20said%2C%20she%20credits%20the%20faculty%20at%20NID%20who%20chipped%20in%20to%20mentor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20its%20prototype%20version%20%E2%80%94%20which%20Komal%20says%20resembled%20a%20bulky%20tiffin%20box%20%E2%80%94%20to%20the%20final%20version%20developed%20a%20year%20later%2C%20which%20is%20sleekness%20personified%2C%20Novocarry%20has%20had%20a%20life%20of%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%202023%20study%2C%20101%20million%20people%20in%20India%20%E2%80%94%2011.4%20percent